data.text:
Jayam Kondaan

Arjun is an NRI IT professional returns to Chennai to set up his own business. He has many friends such as Krishna, Gopal and their respective wives, who make merry. Arjun's philosophy in life is to be always cool and never lose one's temper under any circumstances. But life has many challenges which shall test the very boundaries of Arjun’s strength of character.
